      "updated": 1782208005558,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Databricks Data Prep Jobs\n- DLT / Workflows / streaming or batch\n- enrich raw data with order/sample/test rig dims\n- maintain app-facing serving datasets\n- incremental CDC/window recompute\n\nOutputs:\n- metadata tables\n- page summary tables\n- 1m/5m/15m/1h timeseries tables",
