      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Timeseries Serving Layer\nPreferred path:\n- pre-aggregated Delta tables first\n- move to ClickHouse / Timescale / Lakebase if needed\n\nStores chart-ready buckets:\n- order_id + bucket_start\n- min/max/avg\n- common signals\n- time bounds / grain metadata",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Timeseries Serving Layer\nPreferred path:\n- pre-aggregated Delta tables first\n- move to ClickHouse / Timescale / Lakebase if needed\n\nStores chart-ready buckets:\n- order_id + bucket_start\n- min/max/avg\n- common signals\n- time bounds / grain metadata",
