      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Recommended stack choice: React + TypeScript frontend, FastAPI backend, Databricks pipelines, pre-aggregated serving\ntables first in Delta, Postgres/Lakebase for app metadata, optional ClickHouse if timeseries serving still needs lower\nlatency. Main design rule: do not aggregate raw 1s data during user interactions.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Recommended stack choice: React + TypeScript frontend, FastAPI backend, Databricks pipelines, pre-aggregated serving tables first in Delta, Postgres/Lakebase for app metadata, optional ClickHouse if timeseries serving still needs lower latency. Main design rule: do not aggregate raw 1s data during user interactions.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "aK",
      "autoResize": false
    },
